Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:12.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,At the Grand Temple, we will perform our last Ri Maajon as Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:16.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:18.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Hearing.
